query:
WITH latest AS (
                SELECT id FROM working_commits
                WHERE database_id = $1 AND branch_name = $2 AND status = 'active'
                ORDER BY updated_at DESC
                LIMIT 1
            )
            UPDATE working_commits
            SET status = 'abandoned'
            WHERE database_id = $1
              AND branch_name = $2
              AND status = 'active'
              AND id NOT IN (SELECT id FROM latest)
